The '''1986 Tel Aviv Open''' was a [[tennis]] tournament played on [[hard court]]s that was part of the [[1986 Nabisco Grand Prix]]. It was played at the [[Israel Tennis Centers]] at [[Ramat HaSharon]] near [[Tel Aviv]] in [[Israel]] from October 6 through October 13, 1986.

==Champions==
===Men's Singles===
{{main|1986 Tel Aviv Open – Singles}}
{{flagicon|USA}} '''[[Brad Gilbert]]''' defeated {{flagicon|USA}} [[Aaron Krickstein]] 7&ndash;5, 6&ndash;2
* It was Gilbert's 4th title of the year and the 11th of his career.

===Men's Doubles===
{{main|1986 Tel Aviv Open – Doubles}}
{{flagicon|USA}} '''[[John Letts (tennis)|John Letts]]''' / {{flagicon|SWE}} '''[[Peter Lundgren]]''' defeated {{flagicon|RSA|1928}} [[Christo Steyn]] / {{flagicon|RSA|1928}} [[Danie Visser]] 6&ndash;3, 3&ndash;6, 6&ndash;3
* It was Letts' only title of the year and the 1st of his career. It was Lundgren's only title of the year and the 2nd of his career.

