The '''Gabon Davis Cup team''' represents [[Gabon]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Fédération Gabonaise de Tennis]].
Their best result was finishing third in Pool B of Group III in [[2003 Davis Cup|2003]].
==History== Gabon competed in its first Davis Cup in [[2001 Davis Cup|2001]]. They have not competed since [[2004 Davis Cup|2004]], but are entered in the [[2007 Davis Cup|2007]] competition.
