==International competition== Italian Gymnastics Federation is a member of the European umbrella organization [[European Union of Gymnastics]] as well as the World Association for [[International Gymnastics Federation]]
On the part of the [[Italian Olympic Committee]], the Italian Gymnastics Federation is the only Gymnastics Association authorized to send athletes to the [[Olympic Games]].
